view.name: AH Monthly Provisional Counts of Deaths for Select Causes of Death by Age, and Race and Hispanic Origin
view.description: Provisional counts of deaths by the month the deaths occurred, by age group and race/ethnicity, for select underlying causes of death for 2020-2021. Final data is provided for 2019. The dataset also includes monthly provisional counts of death for COVID-19, coded to ICD-10 code U07.1 as an underlying or multiple cause of death.
